[Note comment in previous post that "children as young as 3 will start receiving COVID-19 vaccines in China...and 2 years old in Cuba" compared with the proposed 5-year-old lower limit for children in the USA. The children in the USA will receive one-third the dose of older children and adults. It is not clear what dose is being administered in China and Cuba to these very young children. Vaccination of children will help protect vulnerable individuals who cannot get vaccinated and will help slow virus spread in general to everyone. - Mod.LK]

